Prints Ki and σ from a FitSigma.batch object

Source: R/print.FitSigma.batch.R
print.FitSigma.batch.Rd

print.FitSigma.batch prints to console the seed lot constant (Ki) and the period to lose unit probit viability (σ).

# S3 method for FitSigma.batch
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

An object of class print.FitSigma.batch.
...

Unused

Value

The Ki and σ values (degree Celsius) in the console.
